snippet.title: Dragon Spirits Release Date Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Dragon Spritis will officially launch on April 25th, 2023. The price will be 9.99 USD and you can enjoy a 20% off discount on the launch week.

While constantly working on a video game without any rest, a college student who's about to graduate quietly slipped into slumber several times. In those lucid dreams, he found himself in the game he was working on, the fantasy world of Dragon Spirits.

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1074190/Dragon_Spirits/
